item.description: Name: Bolun Zhang EID: bz4392 NAme: Zixiang Meng zEID: m4739 Title and Introduction In this project, we choose to discuss the data from the recent Winter Olympic Games which happened in China. For this project, we selected 3 specific datasets, where one contains information about athletes, one contains information about coaches, and one contains information about medals.
